---
applyTo: '**'
description: UI standards
alwaysApply: true
---

UI must be passive.

UI only:

- Displays data
- Sends user intent

UI never:

- Saves data
- Calculates rewards
- Modifies inventory

Flow:

UI
 ->
Controller
 ->
Remote
 ->
Service

Use reusable UI components.

Avoid duplicated UI logic.